  ROLL_DIRECTION (LEFT|RIGHT|DOWN|UP|DOWNLEFT|DOWNRIGHT|UPLEFT|UPRIGHT)
  ROLL_WRAP (ON|OFF)
  BLUR_CENTERWEIGHT val
  BLUR_THRESHOLD val
  DISPLACE_RADIUS val
  DISPLACE_PROBABILITY val
  DISPLACE_SEED
  ROTATE_CENTREX val
  ROTATE_CENTREY val
  ROTATE_RADIUS val
  ROTATE_AMOUNT val
  ROTATE_BRADIUS val
  RIPPLE_CENTREX val
  RIPPLE_CENTREY val
  RIPPLE_SPEED val
  RIPPLE_PERIOD val
  RIPPLE_AMPLITUDE val
  RIPPLE_PHASE val
  RIPPLE_FRAME val
  RIPPLE_TYPE (CONSTANT|INCREASE|DECREASE)
  RIPPLE_RAMP val
  RIPPLE_LEVELOFF val

 Custom-Windows:
  CW_CLOSE name
  CW_OPEN name
  CW_MOVE name x y
  CW_ADD name width height
  CW_KILL name
  CW_ADDGADGET window (STRING|BUTTON|SWITCH) left top width name [action]
  CW_GETGADGET window name
  CW_SETGADGET window name value
  CW_WAITGADGET window name
  CW_ADDTEXT window left top pen text
  CW_ADDLINE window x1 y1 x2 y2 pen
  CW_ADDRECT window left top width height pen (NORMAL|FILLED|BBOX|BBOX2)
  CW_DRAWTEXT window left top pen text
  CW_DRAWLINE window x1 y1 x2 y2 pen
  CW_DRAWRECT window left top width height pen (NORMAL|FILLED|BBOX|BBOX2)
  CW_SAVE name
  CW_LOAD name
  CW_WAIT name
  CW_ISOPEN name
